ansitions were calculated by numerically solving the\none-dimensional Schr\\\"odinger equation using a finite-differences method. Our\nresults are useful for interpretation of the transitions occurring in both,\nsymmetric and asymmetric DQWs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 18:41:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-16"}
