ty, we perform extensive studies of TVT on four benchmarks and the\nexperimental results demonstrate that TVT attains significant improvements\ncompared to existing state-of-the-art UDA methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 22:37:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Nov 2021 18:24:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-29"}
