e impacts of extreme weather events on vulnerable populations; in\nparticular, the findings could provide insights allowing infrastructure\noperators to enhance social equality considerations during managed service\ndisruptions in such events. The results and findings demonstrate the value of\ncommunity-scale big data sources for rapid impact assessment in the aftermath\nof extreme weather events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2021 03:46:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 14:23:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2021 20:01:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
