on to\nfirst approximate the geometry and electronic properties of actinides which are\ndifficult to synthesize or characterize; but knowing that the higher levels of\ntheory, like the 4c-DHF, gives closer results to experiments than the scalar\nDFT-ZORA. We also performed spin-free calculations of geometric parameters for\nthe Americium and Berkelium compounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2021 04:36:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 19:04:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 23:41:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-21"}
