 star formation. This suggests that the hierarchical model\nalone, which explains the populations of other parts of the same association,\nis not sufficient to explain its whole formation history.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:36:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
